task.summary: Second commit - changes scraper and test_scraper, file structure

Refactor cleaning pipeline and add robust quality + testing tools
- Split `cleaning_pipeline.py` into strict cleaning logic only (removed classification) - Created `data_quality_report.py` to generate file-level data quality diagnostics - Added `label_keywords.py` stub for future NLP feature extraction - Implemented `test_cleaning.py`: - tests `clean_question` normalization - tests full `clean_all_raw_files()` pipeline with mock input - verifies filtered output and logging - Minor updates to `scraper.py` and `test_scraper.py` for integration and stability - Removed legacy `clean_questions.py` (superseded)
